<b>Marine Headquarters
New World</b>

222
00:12:49.000 --> 00:12:50.750
Report for Fleet Admiral Sakazuki!

223
00:12:51.130 --> 00:12:53.960
The Kingdoms of Tajine and Eigis are revolting!

224
00:12:53.960 --> 00:12:57.920
Just crush every last one of them!

225
00:12:57.920 --> 00:13:00.090
Hurry up! Get a move on!

226
00:13:04.760 --> 00:13:07.470
Deploy every seraphim!

227
00:13:07.850 --> 00:13:10.940
Crocodile has appeared on Empty Bluffs Island!

228
00:13:11.560 --> 00:13:14.610
The Marines found themselves stretched thin...

229
00:13:15.190 --> 00:13:19.030
